    "description": "——游戏时长20h，一段充满谜题的旅途。<br>——迷你团队用爱发电三年之作，完全自由探索的小型开放世界。<br><br><strong>★公主，踏上归途</strong><br>在公主的王国面临危机之时，世界之神却把公主带到了一个与世隔绝的奇幻世界。公主不愿一人如此活着，为了打通回家之路，她踏上了新的冒险。<br>在《Light Tracer 2》中，你将操纵公主和悬在空中的“光之手”，在4座不同的岛屿和公主的王国中解谜冒险。你将看到布满苔藓的遗迹、迸发的熔岩、神秘的地下城……只有通过挑战、点燃光柱，运用智慧和勇气才能回到王国，直面神明，得知世界的真相。<br><br><strong>★探索</strong><br>在开放世界中，按照自己的节奏探索4座截然不同的岛屿和王国中的地下城。在绝景中驾驶小船或奔跑穿行，自由探索世界。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1085930/extras/42a5f907ea90498129f0cc5868b68e44.poster.avif?t=1636091970\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1085930/extras/42a5f907ea90498129f0cc5868b68e44.webm?t=1636091970\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1085930/extras/42a5f907ea90498129f0cc5868b68e44.mp4?t=1636091970\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>★解谜</strong><br>同时操纵公主和“光之手”，完成视角切换，配合解谜。或是依靠重力、浮力等物理特性，准确把握机关运转的时机，运用潜行或射击元素解开谜题。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1085930/extras/47b67a3a3a6c2b49fd36e841cff9249c.poster.avif?t=1636091970\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1085930/extras/47b67a3a3a6c2b49fd36e841cff9249c.webm?t=1636091970\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1085930/extras/47b67a3a3a6c2b49fd36e841cff9249c.mp4?t=1636091970\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>★战斗</strong><br>本作的战斗有一点点【魂】味，强调攻击和闪避时机的把握，总的来说相当硬核难度也颇高，是整个游戏“充满挑战”设计理念里重要的一环。公主可以利用神剑或弓箭战斗，配合特殊情况下触发的QTE反击，并利用道具的冰冻、吹风、滚石等能力配合战斗。<br>但是如果觉得吃力，也可以打开简单模式，享受切菜的快感，同时专注解谜和剧情的推进！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1085930/extras/1a9d36d5960b68c799c1a0fb96caa389.poster.avif?t=1636091970\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1085930/extras/1a9d36d5960b68c799c1a0fb96caa389.webm?t=1636091970\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1085930/extras/1a9d36d5960b68c799c1a0fb96caa389.mp4?t=1636091970\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>★真相</strong><br>这个与世隔绝的世界与王国之间是什么关系？王国面临的灾难是什么？神为什么会准确知道这一切？只能靠公主勇敢地探索和发现。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1085930/extras/d4a167edf6e279f63513e771ecc3911e.poster.avif?t=1636091970\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1085930/extras/d4a167edf6e279f63513e771ecc3911e.webm?t=1636091970\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1085930/extras/d4a167edf6e279f63513e771ecc3911e.mp4?t=1636091970\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>★唯美</strong><br>被岁月侵蚀的遗迹、世界尽头的火山熔岩、一望无垠的荒漠、东方的水之都、王国的地下城……精致的画面与奇幻的色彩，一幅唯美又惊心动魄的画卷呈现在你的眼前。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1085930/extras/660dd3dc1f3f65ff323bc139b9b8abc8.poster.avif?t=1636091970\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1085930/extras/660dd3dc1f3f65ff323bc139b9b8abc8.webm?t=1636091970\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1085930/extras/660dd3dc1f3f65ff323bc139b9b8abc8.mp4?t=1636091970\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
